{"tid":2294280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Twitter稱會將美國總統官方帳戶移交拜登使用","createTime":"2020-11-21T02:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T03:49:32.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2be090200b09ae58bbbe0ed7cb686a172f203621","tid":2294280,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:02:18.000Z","msg":"Twitter稱會將美國總統官方帳戶移交拜登使用<br />\n<br />\n個人社交網站Twitter表示，會在明年1月20日美國總統就職日，將美國總統的Twitter官方帳號，移交民主黨拜登使用，其他白宮的官方帳號亦會在同日移交。Twitter表示，正積極為美國政府官方帳號的過渡提供支援，並與美國國家檔案局密切協商，確保在總統就職日所有官方帳號能順利移交。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2367254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2367254&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3zsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=77832a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2367254</a>"},{"pid":"5198badbb1e11a36b783aed136810dbe844a3afc","tid":2294280,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:03:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d909e8c054ac161c0ce5b5aa44a9c0c3e2b99f5","tid":2294280,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:04:26.000Z","msg":"做撚埋啲小動作"},{"pid":"ee4b6470bc26fb939c62ff5380506b51780fa421","tid":2294280,"uid":383914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:04:26.000Z","msg":"Twitter總統：拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35537b8e8289691fa9f768f11e6c218a308fdec","tid":2294280,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a907a5a46096df88206f095406a9f0a0a